    <item>
      <title>日经指数因美国经济衰退忧虑跌至三周低点；芯片股下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/japanese-stocks-set-to-slide-as-yen-strength-weighs-on-exporters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本股市下跌，日经 225 股票平均指数跌至三周低点，因美国就业数据疲软引发对全球最大经济体经济放缓的担忧。芯片相关股票领跌，而金融股则受到债券收益率下降的打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/japanese-stocks-set-to-slide-as-yen-strength-weighs-on-exporters</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 23:36:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受美国库存下降迹象影响，油价跌至 14 个月低点附近</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-5</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于一份行业报告指出美国原油库存大幅减少，油价稳定在 2023 年 6 月以来的最低收盘价附近，市场在本周大幅抛售后稍事休息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-5</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 23:29:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
